    • 方法详细资料

      • calculateAmount

        public void calculateAmount()
        Calculate prizeAmount/taxAmount/taxAmount based on List<PrizeLevelItemDto>.

        This method should be called after setLevelItems. Due to PrizeLevel and PrizeLevelItemDto are managed by JPA runtime, when initialize PrizeLevel, the runtime will set a List of 0 elements to it, that is why we can't calculate XXX_amount in setLevelItems()

        Besides call this method will force runtime to retrieve the entity PrizeLevelItemDto from underlying database, not just a proxy.
